---
title: Kumara & Candied Pecan Salad with Avocado & Goat Cheese
description: A feast for the eyes as well as the stomach, this salad is a true celebration of the sweet nuttiness that can be found in a savoury dish. Between creamy kumara and avocado, goat cheese and crunchy candied pecans, you won’t be able to decide what to eat first!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/5bb41c2530006c49b4065194-a5b222c0.jpg
